title: Ravens-Jets TNF Recap, Lamar further cements MVP (Football 12/13)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough to react to the Ravens victory over the Jets on Thursday Night Football (:20). The guys discuss another miraculous and record-setting performance by Lamar Jackson, the Ravens transforming football, Adam Gase's ineptitude, Sam Darnold's struggles and more.
